description: Try our easy to follow Cheese & Vegetable Noodle Bake recipe. Absolutely delicious with the best ingredients from Woolworths.
keywords: Vegetable bake,Zucchini,High protein,Tree nut free,Spring,Low sugar,Chicken,Sesame free,Peanut free
name: Cheese & Vegetable Noodle Bake Recipe | Woolworths

recipeInstructions.text: Preheat oven to 180°C/160°C fan forced. Grease and line a 28cm x 18cm lamington pan with baking paper.

Cook Maggi 2-minute noodles chicken according to packet directions (do not add flavour sachet at this stage); drain. Add to a large bowl with flavour sachet, zucchini, carrot, onion, eggs and 3/4 cup (90g) of the cheese; mix well.
Pour into prepared pan and sprinkle with remaining cheese; bake for 30 minutes or until golden.
